name: Sprott Physical Uranium Trust
longDescription: The Sprott Physical Uranium Trust seeks to provide a secure, convenient and exchange-traded investment alternative for investors interested in holding uranium.  The Sprott Physical Uranium Trust invests and holds substantially all of its assets in uranium in the form of U3O8.
